{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Re:END is a laid-back, top-down, solo mode RPG, like the great MMOs of the good old days. Re:END is easy to operate, and has a deep system, including leveling up, reincarnation, pets, equipment upgrades, arenas, materials, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience an RPG with all the elements that made the good old days (late 2000s) MMORPGs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25bcLeveling up and reincarnation</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What would an MMO be without leveling up? Nothing beats the feeling of overcoming adversity, discovering new and better ways to earn experience points, and getting stronger with every level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Allocate status points every time you level up, recalibrate, and reincarnate. Get stronger and develop your character to be who you are.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25bcCollecting materials and upgrading weapons</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect materials by defeating powerful monsters or fishing to improve your equipment. Fight more powerful monsters, face new challenges, and prepare for the next power spike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25bcPets</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All enemies, including bosses, can become your allies (some arena monsters cannot join). When you defeat an enemy, there is a small 0.3% chance that it will become your ally. The probability may be low, but the sense of accomplishment when it happens is exceptional!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080820/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735032790","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080820/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1735032790","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080820/c072df7e6e2455657c643492e5905d061c7f5f6e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735032790","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080820/c072df7e6e